{"tid":583720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"習大大到底睇到葉蔚琳慘況未","createTime":"2018-03-07T08:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T08:44:49.000Z","uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42caf1acfc82cdab1516279425306da6360cfa80","tid":583720,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"大埔死傷者真係好撚慘<br />\n應聚焦善後時 俾隻癲婆發死人財<br />\n死咬調整方案不公 根本個個有得益<br />\n人地覺得佢on9又覺得係打壓<br />\n大大聲聲嗌 死而無憾又出黎懶地硬<br />\n<br />\n最嘔心一副喊晒咀臉求習雜<br />\n講副尾又係為錢 仲要自己計錯數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/164031_38bba97cdba48391aa425355635b45e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F164031_38bba97cdba48391aa425355635b45e5.png&h=264a5e11&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}